    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Guidance on Converting Parallel Distribution Notices (PDNs) to UK Parallel Import Licences (PILs) in a no deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The process to convert Parallel Distribution Notices (PDNs) into Parallel Import Licences (PILs) if there is a no-deal Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

